text: Very clean and neat station and it is located near lots of Condos. You can reach Bugis in 20~30 mins only. Very convenient
The toilets are clean. And most importantly, have toilet paper in each cubicle instead of making you purchase a pack of tissue paper outside first.

Great and easy way to get around, give it a try, don't be afraid it's simple to navigate.
Love the MRT clean and modern.
New and convenient, walkable diatance to HillV2 and rail malls. Direct way to downtown, bugis & raffles. Less people and quiet station. Pretty cool name also.
Take 2 times elevator. Understand why many people prefer taking the lift
